    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COOKIE TOWN UNDER SIEGE!</strong> 🍪⚠️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Disaster has struck <strong>Cookie Town!</strong> The once-sweet and peaceful city is being devoured by dancing, cookie-eating monsters! With the town’s <strong>legendary Broccoli </strong>shattered and scattered, nothing is stopping the crazed horde. As the towns last hope, you must <strong>grapple, shoot, and puzzle-solve</strong> your way through the chaos—recovering lost broccolis, fighting monsters, and mastering physics-based challenges to save Cookie Town before it crumbles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪝 <strong>Grapple, Swing &amp; Soar!</strong> – Use your physics-based grappling hook to zip through Cookie Town, dodge monsters, and recover Broccoli!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/f3c8751b23471e0b72974730bf6be957.poster.avif?t=1751895081\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/f3c8751b23471e0b72974730bf6be957.webm?t=1751895081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/f3c8751b23471e0b72974730bf6be957.mp4?t=1751895081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍪 <strong>Cookie-Chomping Chaos!</strong> – Face an army of unpredictable, dancing, and dangerously hungry monsters who won’t stop until every crumb of Cookie Town is devoured!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/3c910ea7731f747340d1bcb2df7c3010.poster.avif?t=1751895081\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/3c910ea7731f747340d1bcb2df7c3010.webm?t=1751895081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/3c910ea7731f747340d1bcb2df7c3010.mp4?t=1751895081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 <strong>Complete Wacky Challenges!</strong> – Take on bizarre physics-based puzzles and absurd objectives to recover all the missing Broccoli pieces</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/5eb4fa3e411e20306a12b652ce0f46c0.poster.avif?t=1751895081\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/5eb4fa3e411e20306a12b652ce0f46c0.webm?t=1751895081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142130/extras/5eb4fa3e411e20306a12b652ce0f46c0.mp4?t=1751895081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
